{"tid":2305393,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"末日博士：別買比特幣　它像在受操縱賭場裏賭錢","createTime":"2020-11-29T14:56:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T05:33:01.000Z","uid":66271,"like":14,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"63810345c6061269aa0877fc1ff1b8e60ef5bdae","tid":2305393,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T14:56:34.000Z","msg":"外國傳媒報道，曾準確預測2008年金融海嘯、有「末日博士」之稱的紐約大學經濟學教授魯比尼近日批評，虛擬貨幣「一哥」比特幣價格受嚴重操縱，投資比特幣等同在一個受操縱的賭場裏賭博，呼籲投資者應遠離。<br />\n<br />\n他說：「大量抱有FOMO(驚死買唔切)情緒的白癡散戶再次投資比特幣，機構或散戶在投資組合中放入加密貨幣，就像他們在2017年底所做的那樣，當時比特幣從10,000美元漲至19,000美元，但在2019年跌至3,000美元，唯一的贏家是那些操縱市場的『鯨魚』，它們把自己的比特幣拋售給那些白癡散戶，導致比特幣暴跌85%。」<br />\n<br />\n魯比尼認為，與股票、債券、房地產等能產生收入的資產相比，比特幣毫無內在價值，且加密貨幣交易所也充斥可疑的交易行為。"},{"pid":"c11f13a2d554a08f716b9fc902013e95c50cf516","tid":2305393,"uid":6030,"like":37,"dislike":3,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T14:58:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VUZRE81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVUZRE81.jpg&h=cc519bd4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f4a76e8681676ec6c21932b0bbfba2550fc8c83","tid":2305393,"uid":41524,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T14:59:35.000Z","msg":"咁開short囉"},{"pid":"672af0213146d92230862e2012efb551c6f0043f","tid":2305393,"uid":73241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4f4a76e8681676ec6c21932b0bbfba2550fc8c83","tid":2305393,"uid":41524,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T14:59:35.000Z","msg":"咁開short囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T15:00:15.000Z","msg":"夾到你上10萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b94f6ec785df5d51a4c602a6fbb0bf509b3ded9f","tid":2305393,"uid":98887,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T15:06:41.000Z","msg":"末日博士收得皮未"},{"pid":"df8d4198fd32f14946b4dd5ff2103cc67b7a60d7","tid":2305393,"uid":5166,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f4a76e8681676ec6c21932b0bbfba2550fc8c83","tid":2305393,"u